'''''Ing Alino ning Angin''''' ('''''The Shadow of the Wind''''') ({{lang-es|'''La sombra del viento'''}}) metung yang [[nobela]]ng sinulat na aniang 2001 [[novel]] ning talasulat ning Espaniang i [[Carlos Ruiz Zafón]], a metung a bestseller king mabilug a yatu. Liniikas ne king English aniang 2004 [[Lucia Graves]], at maigit lang metung a miliun deng misali king UK mu. Bayu ita, migtagumpe ne king mismung Europa (mainland Europe), at pilan yang domingung mumuna kareng listaan da reng bestseller king Espania. Kaibat nang milikas aniang 2004, linimbag neng pasibayu king Estados Unidos ning [[Penguin Books]] ampo king Britania ning [[Weidenfeld & Nicolson]] ampo ning [[Orion Books]]. 

King kayang sariling ciudad o lakanbalen ning Barcelona, a malinong milarawan king libru, gewa rang pisasabian deng makabalen a Catalan (Catalan nationalists) ing pamangamit nang Ruiz king amanung Castila at ali king Catalan.<ref>Graham Keeley, "The Emperor's New Clothes: Catalan nationalism"
[http://www.expatica.com/es/articles/news/the-emperors-new-clothes:-catalan-nationalism-25223.html]; "Spanish writers snub invite to Frankfurt fair in spat over Catalan nationalism" [http://ca.news.yahoo.com/s/capress/070808/entertainment/books_spain_book_spat].</ref> 

Ing sabik dang tatalukian a katuki ning nobela, metung yang prequel king ''Ing Alino ning Angin'', a linimbag na king Castila ning Planeta aniang Abril 2008. Ikua na ning [[Weidenfeld & Nicolson]] ing katuliran ning pamaglikas, at milimbag ya ing hardback English edition aniang Junio 2009. Maki pamagat yang ''The Angel's Game'' o ''Pialung ning Anghel'', at miliari ya king Barcelona kanitang decadang 1920 ampong 1930. Tungkul ya king kayanakan a talasulat a lepitan ning misteriosong tauan at papasulatan neng libru. Linikas ne murin king English Lucia Graves ing ''Pialung ning Anghel''. 

